&lt;section id="win11gtk4"&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a class="toc-backref" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#toc-entry-1" role="doc-backlink"&gt;еңЁWin11дёҠе®үиЈ…GTK4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;nav class="contents" id="topic-1"&gt;
&lt;p class="topic-title"&gt;зӣ®еҪ•&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class="simple"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference internal" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#win11gtk4" id="toc-entry-1"&gt;еңЁWin11дёҠе®үиЈ…GTK4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference internal" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#section-1" id="toc-entry-2"&gt;е®үиЈ…иҝҮзЁӢ&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference internal" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#msys2" id="toc-entry-3"&gt;1. дёӢиҪҪе№¶е®үиЈ…Msys2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference internal" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#gkt4toolchain" id="toc-entry-4"&gt;2. е®үиЈ…GKT4еә“е’Ңtoolchain&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference internal" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#path" id="toc-entry-5"&gt;3. и®ҫзҪ®Path&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference internal" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#hello-world" id="toc-entry-6"&gt;4. Hello World&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference internal" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#section-2" id="toc-entry-7"&gt;жҖ»з»“&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/nav&gt;
&lt;p&gt;жң¬ж–ҮеҢ…жӢ¬дәҶдҪңиҖ…еңЁе®үиЈ…иҝҮзЁӢдёӯйҒҮеҲ°зҡ„еқ‘...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;е®үиЈ…иҝҮзЁӢеңЁзҡ„SandboxйҮҢз»ҸиҝҮжөӢиҜ•:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;aside class="admonition note"&gt;
&lt;p class="admonition-title"&gt;жіЁи§Ј&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Edition Windows 11 Enterprise&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Version 22H2&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;OS build        22621.1848&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/aside&gt;
&lt;aside class="admonition hint"&gt;
&lt;p class="admonition-title"&gt;жҸҗзӨә&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference external" href="https://www.gtk.org/docs/installations/windows/#using-gtk-from-msys2-packages"&gt;GKTе®ҳзҪ‘зҡ„е®үиЈ…жҢҮеҚ—&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/aside&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;section id="section-1"&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a class="toc-backref" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#toc-entry-2" role="doc-backlink"&gt;е®үиЈ…иҝҮзЁӢ&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;section id="msys2"&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;a class="toc-backref" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#toc-entry-3" role="doc-backlink"&gt;1. дёӢиҪҪе№¶е®үиЈ…Msys2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;жң¬ж•ҷзЁӢдҪҝз”Ёй»ҳи®Өе®үиЈ…и·Ҝеҫ„пјҢеҰӮдҪҝз”ЁиҮӘе®ҡд№үпјҢеңЁеҗҺж–Үи®ҫзҪ®PATHж—¶йңҖиҰҒжіЁж„Ҹ&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;д»Һе®ҳзҪ‘дёӢиҪҪ &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://www.msys2.org/"&gt;Msys2&lt;/a&gt;пјҢе№¶е®үиЈ…&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;зӮ№еҮ»FinishеҗҺеј№еҮәе‘Ҫд»ӨиЎҢз•ҢйқўпјҢж №жҚ®Msys2зҡ„ж–ҮжЎЈпјҢжҲ‘д»¬йҰ–е…Ҳе®үиЈ…gcc&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;aside class="admonition note"&gt;
&lt;p class="admonition-title"&gt;жіЁи§Ј&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;еӣҪеҶ…з”ЁжҲ·еҸҜиғҪйңҖиҰҒжӣҙжҚўеӣҪеҶ…жәҗжҸҗеҚҮдёӢиҪҪйҖҹеәҰпјҢ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;иҝҷйҮҢжҲ‘д»¬дҪҝз”Ё &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/help/msys2/"&gt;жё…еҚҺеӨ§еӯҰй•ңеғҸз«ҷ&lt;/a&gt; ,еңЁз»Ҳз«Ҝиҫ“е…Ҙ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;sed &lt;span class="pre"&gt;-i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="pre"&gt;"s#https\?://mirror.msys2.org/#https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/msys2/#g"&lt;/span&gt; /etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist*&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;е®ҢжҲҗжҚўжәҗ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/aside&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;pacman &lt;span class="pre"&gt;-S&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="pre"&gt;mingw-w64-ucrt-x86_64-gcc&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="/images/Msys2_install.png" class="align-center" src="https://bajzc.com/images/Msys2_install.png"&gt;
&lt;dl&gt;
&lt;dt&gt;еӣһиҪҰејҖе§Ӣе®үиЈ…&lt;/dt&gt;
&lt;dd&gt;&lt;aside class="admonition hint"&gt;
&lt;p class="admonition-title"&gt;жҸҗзӨә&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;еңЁMsys2 ShellйҮҢзҡ„еӨҚеҲ¶еҸҜд»Ҙеҝ«жҚ·й”®Shift+Ins&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/aside&gt;
&lt;/dd&gt;
&lt;/dl&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;section id="gkt4toolchain"&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;a class="toc-backref" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#toc-entry-4" role="doc-backlink"&gt;2. е®үиЈ…GKT4еә“е’Ңtoolchain&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;иҰҒе®үиЈ…GKT4пјҢеңЁз»Ҳз«Ҝиҫ“е…Ҙ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;pacman &lt;span class="pre"&gt;-S&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="pre"&gt;mingw-w64-x86_64-gtk4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;дёәдәҶеңЁwindowsдёҠдҪҝз”ЁGNU/makeпјҢиҫ“е…Ҙ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;pacman &lt;span class="pre"&gt;-S&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="pre"&gt;mingw-w64-x86_64-toolchain&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="pre"&gt;base-devel&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;йғҪжҳҜдёҖи·ҜеӣһиҪҰйҖүжӢ©й»ҳи®Ө&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;img alt="/images/Msys2_tool-chain.png" class="align-center" src="https://bajzc.com/images/Msys2_tool-chain.png"&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;section id="path"&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;a class="toc-backref" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#toc-entry-5" role="doc-backlink"&gt;3. и®ҫзҪ®Path&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;жү“ејҖ &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://www.baidu.com/baidu?ie=utf-8&amp;amp;wd=path%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE"&gt;Pathи®ҫзҪ®&lt;/a&gt;  з»ҶиҠӮдёҚиөҳиҝ°&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;еңЁзі»з»ҹеҸҳйҮҸйҮҢжүҫеҲ°Path,жү“ејҖеҗҺеҠ дёҠдҪ зҡ„е®үиЈ…и·Ҝеҫ„ &lt;em&gt;mingw64bin&lt;/em&gt; пјҢпјҲеҜ№жҲ‘жқҘиҜҙе°ұжҳҜ &lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;&lt;span class="pre"&gt;C:\msys64\mingw64\bin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt; пјү&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;еҶҚж–°е»әдёҖдёӘ &lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;&lt;span class="pre"&gt;C:\msys64\usr\bin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;пјҢзӮ№еҮ»зЎ®е®ҡдҝқеӯҳгҖӮ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;aside class="admonition note"&gt;
&lt;p class="admonition-title"&gt;жіЁи§Ј&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;иҝҷйҮҢеҚғдёҮиҰҒжіЁж„ҸйЎәеәҸпјҢеӣ дёәWindowsдјҡдҫқз…§PATHд»ҺеүҚеҲ°еҗҺжү«жҸҸгҖӮиҝҷеҜ№д№ӢеҗҺзҡ„ &lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;&lt;span class="pre"&gt;pkg-config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt; д»ҘеҸҠ &lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;mkdir&lt;/code&gt; йғҪжңүеҪұе“Қ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/aside&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;з”ұдәҺжҲ‘д»¬иҰҒдҪҝз”Ё &lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;make&lt;/code&gt; е‘Ҫд»Ө,иҖҢMsys2й»ҳи®ӨжҠҠе®ғе‘ҪеҗҚдёә"mingw32-make"гҖӮжүҖд»ҘжҲ‘д»¬иҝӣе…ҘеҲҡеҲҡиҫ“е…Ҙзҡ„зӣ®еҪ•пјҲC:/msys64/mingw64/binпјүпјҢжүҫеҲ° &lt;em&gt;mingw32-make&lt;/em&gt; йҮҚе‘ҪеҗҚпјҲжҲ–иҖ…ctrl+c,ctrl+vз”ҹжҲҗдёҖдёӘеүҜжң¬пјүпјҢе‘ҪеҗҚдёәmakeгҖӮ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;жӯӨж—¶жҲ‘д»¬еҶҚжү“ејҖcmd(Win+R)пјҢиҫ“е…Ҙ &lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;make &lt;span class="pre"&gt;-v&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt; ,еҸ‘зҺ°е·Із»ҸеҸҜд»ҘиҝҗиЎҢдәҶгҖӮ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;жҺҘзқҖеҶҚеңЁcmdдёӯиҜ•дёҖдёӢе‘Ҫд»Ө &lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;&lt;span class="pre"&gt;pkg-config&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="pre"&gt;--cflags&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="pre"&gt;--libs&lt;/span&gt; gtk4&lt;/code&gt; пјҢеҰӮжһңжңүзұ»дјјдёӢйқўзҡ„иҫ“еҮәпјҢе°ұиҜҙжҳҺжҲҗеҠҹдәҶпјҡ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;img alt="/images/cmd_pkg-config.png" class="align-center" src="https://bajzc.com/images/cmd_pkg-config.png"&gt;
&lt;aside class="admonition hint"&gt;
&lt;p class="admonition-title"&gt;жҸҗзӨә&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;еҰӮжһңжІЎжңүпјҢйӮЈд№ҲеҸҜд»ҘиҜҙдҪ дёҚе№ёйҒҮеҲ°дәҶз¬¬дёҖдёӘеқ‘,е’ҢдҪңиҖ…дёҖж ·пјҲ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;йҰ–е…Ҳз»ҷMSжүЈ &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://img.devrant.com/devrant/rant/r_1093122_83dS9.jpg"&gt;666&lt;/a&gt; пјҲиҸң&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;жү“ејҖMsys2 ShellпјҢиҝҗиЎҢ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;cp &lt;span class="pre"&gt;-r&lt;/span&gt; /mingw64/lib/pkgconfig/* /usr/share/pkgconfig/&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;иҝҷе°ұдјҡжҠҠе®ғжҸҗзӨәзҡ„"gtk4.pc"д»ҘеҸҠе…¶д»–дёҖзі»еҲ—дҫқиө–пјҢеӨҚеҲ¶еҲ° &lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;&lt;span class="pre"&gt;pkg-config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt; дјҡиҮӘеҠЁжү«жҸҸзҡ„ж–Үд»¶еӨ№дёӢгҖӮ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/aside&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;section id="hello-world"&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;a class="toc-backref" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#toc-entry-6" role="doc-backlink"&gt;4. Hello World&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ж–°е»әдёҖдёӘж–Үд»¶еӨ№пјҢиҝҷйҮҢе°ұеҸ«demo,еңЁйҮҢйқўеҲӣе»әdemo.c (Shift+еҸій”®ж–Үд»¶иө„жәҗз®ЎзҗҶеҷЁпјҢеңЁиҜҘзӣ®еҪ•дёӢжү“ејҖpowershellпјҢиҫ“е…Ҙ &lt;code class="docutils literal"&gt;notepad demo.c&lt;/code&gt; )&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;иҝҷйҮҢдҪҝз”ЁGTKе®ҳж–№зҡ„е®һдҫӢпјҡ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;div class="code"&gt;&lt;pre class="code C"&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-1" name="rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-1" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="cp"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="cpf"&gt;&amp;lt;gtk/gtk.h&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-2" name="rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-2" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-3" name="rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-3" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;static&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="kt"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nf"&gt;activate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;GtkApplication&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;app&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;gpointer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;user_data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-4" name="rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-4" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-4"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;        &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;GtkWidget&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;window&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-5" name="rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-5" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-5"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-6" name="rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-6" href="https://bajzc.com/zh_cn/posts/install-gtk4-on-windows/#rest_code_c72cff08d81a4309a4fc6cf3c2975f1d-6"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;        &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;window&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;gtk_application_window_new&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;app&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
